title: Gelora Joko Samudro Stadium
text: Gelora Joko Samudro is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in the town of <a href="Kebomas">Kebomas</a>, <a href="Gresik%20Regency">Gresik Regency</a>, <a href="East%20Java">East Java</a>, <a href="Indonesia">Indonesia</a>. It is mostly used for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the new home stadium of <a href="Gresik%20United">Gresik United</a>. The stadium hold 40,000 spectators.
